eve indigestion, acidity, and stomach discomfort.\",\r\n    \"categoryId\": \"014e50b5-423f-4a28-85a7-3336c1219975\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    \"brandName\": \"Alergin\",\r\n    \"genericName\": \"Cetirizine\",\r\n    \"manufacturer\": \"Incepta Pharmaceuticals\",\r\n    \"strength\": \"10mg\",\r\n    \"dosageForm\": \"TABLET\",\r\n    \"unit\": \"tablet\",\r\n    \"packSize\": 10,\r\n    \"dosageInfo\": \"1 tablet once daily at night\",\r\n    \"price\": 30,\r\n    \"piecePrice\": 3,\r\n    \"stockQuantity\": 160,\r\n    \"expiryDate\": \"2027-02-28T00:00:00.000Z\",\r\n    \"image\": \"https://example.com/images/alerzin.jpg\",\r\n    \"description\": \"Antihistamine used for relief from sneezing, itching, watery eyes, and allergic rhinitis.\",\r\n    \"categoryId\": \"9d3462f6-5eeb-4c21-bf5c-59467940a75d\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    \"brandName\": \"Deslor\",\r\n    \"genericName\": \"Desloratadine\",\r\n    \"manufacturer\": \"Beximco Pharmaceuticals\",\r\n    \"strength\": \"5mg\",\r\n    \"dosageForm\": \"TABLET\",\r\n    \"unit\": \"tablet\",\r\n    \"packSize\": 10,\r\n    \"dosageInfo\": \"1 tablet daily\",\r\n    \"price\": 40,\r\n    \"piecePrice\": 4,\r\n    \"stockQuantity\": 140,\r\n    \"expiryDate\": \"2027-01-31T00:00:00.000Z\",\r\n    \"image\": \"https://example.com/images/deslor.jpg\",\r\n    \"description\": \"Non-drowsy antihistamine used to treat seasonal allergies and chronic urticaria.\",\r\n    \"categoryId\": \"9d3462f6-5eeb-4c21-bf5c-59467940a75d\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    \"brandName\": \"Becozyme\",\r\n    \"genericName\": \"Vitamin B Complex\",\r\n    \"manufacturer\": \"Opsonin Pharma\",\r\n    \"strength\": \"B-Complex\",\r\n    \"dosageForm\": \"TABLET\",\r\n    \"unit\": \"tablet\",\r\n    \"packSize\": 20,\r\n    \"dosageInfo\": \"1 tablet daily after meal\",\r\n    \"price\": 60,\r\n    \"piecePrice\": 3,\r\n    \"stockQuantity\": 130,\r\n    \"expiryDate\": \"2027-08-31T00:00:00.000Z\",\r\n    \"image\": \"https://example.com/images/becozyme.